## Folder Structure

```
aioverse-brand-assets-repo/
├── logos/
│   ├── svg/          # Scalable vector logos & marks
│   ├── webp/         # Rasterized WebP logos & marks
│   └── source/       # Editable source files (.ai)
├── icons/            # UI icons & app icon variants
├── social/
│   ├── banners/      # YouTube, Facebook platform banners
│   ├── backgrounds/  # WhatsApp and chat backgrounds
│   └── profile/      # Profile picture assets (pfp)
├── covers/           # Repository / presentation covers
├── colors/           # Color swatch reference images
├── fonts/            # Brand typography packages (.zip)
├── raw/              # Unprocessed source imagery
└── docs/             # Brand documentation & token specs
```

-----

## Naming Convention

All assets follow a unified **kebab-case** pattern:

```
{brand}-{category}-{variant}-{theme}[-{size}][-v{N}].{ext}
```

**Segments:**

|Segment          |Values                                                                                      |
|-----------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|`{brand}`        |`aioverse`, `aiotize`, `font`                                                               |
|`{category}`     |`logo`, `mark`, `icon`, `banner`, `bg`, `pfp`, `cover`, `color`                             |
|`{variant}`      |`full`, `rounded`, `tagline`, `grid`, `gradient`, `youtube`, `facebook`, `whatsapp`, `gmail`|
|`{theme}`        |`electric-aqua`, `midnight-teal`, `soft-white`, `electric-blue`, `gradient`                 |
|`{size}` *(opt.)*|`2560x1440`, `820x312`, `300px`                                                             |
|`{v}` *(opt.)*   |`v1`, `v2`, `v3` — when multiple versions exist                                             |

**Rules:**

- All lowercase, no spaces, no underscores
- Hyphens as the only separator
- SVG and WebP of the same asset share the same base name
- Font files use `font-` prefix

